mimo_tips: The Genshin Impact HoYoWiki is an encyclopedic database built by HoYoLAB and Travelers. Here, we will record as many characters and stories as possible from the world of Teyvat. The online editor is now available, and we welcome enthusiastic Travelers to contact us to enrich the content and correct errors together. Your contributions will be recorded by the HoYoWiki!
